        {
            "title": "財經｜基石藥業(02616)折讓近7%配股籌逾10億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜基石藥業(02616)折讓近7%配股籌逾10億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜基石藥業(02616)折讓近7%配股籌逾10億</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基石藥業(02616)公布，配售1.18億股新股，相當於擴大後股本約7.4%；每股配售價8.97元，較昨日收市價9.64元折讓約6.95%，集資10.58億元，淨額估計為10.53億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司擬將所得款項淨額中，90%用於與集團「管線2.0」中的資產的相關進一步研發；餘下淨額於適當時用於其他一般公司用途。</p></div>",
